1204
01:22:47.015 --> 01:22:49.655
<i>I don't know how long the fit lasted.</i>

1205
01:22:49.815 --> 01:22:51.215
<i>I'd gone mad.</i>

1206
01:22:52.375 --> 01:22:53.815
<i>Completely mad.</i>

1207
01:22:54.935 --> 01:22:57.135
<i>What was I digging for?</i>

1208
01:22:59.535 --> 01:23:01.255
