1282
01:26:34.255 --> 01:26:35.215
You know.

1283
01:26:35.375 --> 01:26:37.935
you asked me
to tell you what I thought.

1284
01:26:38.095 --> 01:26:39.455
No problem.

1285
01:26:43.535 --> 01:26:45.815
